  .section-grouping
    %h2(id="2011062101")
      21st June 2011: Image Factory 0.2.2 now available

    %p
      The Image Factory team is pleased to announce the release of Image
      Factory version 0.2.2.  Version 0.2.2 adds features and bugfixes needed
      to support the next step in the evolution of Aeolus.

    %p
      %ul
        %li
          VMware vSphere support has been added.
        %li
          Support for snapshots of EC2 images on EBS has been added.
        %li
          Importing images from providers has been added to both the command
          line and QMF interfaces.
        %li
          Explicit support for rebuilding images without having to respecify
          the template.
        %li
          Building and pushing images now supports multiple targets or
          providers in a single call rather than requiring one to repeat the
          call multiple times. (added in 0.2.0)
        %li
          Source has been cleaned up and DRYed out.  This is an ongoing,
          iterative process.

    %p
      Download packages from:
